Detailed Description

Class representing a vehicle or a pedestrian.

The vehicle is used to keep track of the current vehicle used by a route to get to a certain point. DriverPref keep track of which vehicle transitions that are possible and also creates the vehicles. Vehicles should only be created by DriverPref.
